						               													<description>Three warriors must save 4 keepers of the castle of light who have turned into evil monsters, and they must try to maintain as many towers to get high scores in their mission.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The gameplay is simple, during 7 rounds any player rolls 5 dice, 2 of them will activate the effects of the managers that can be to destroy towers, bring fog to the towers, among others, then with the 3 remaining dice you can organize their values &amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#139;&amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#139;in one or more rows of actions of the warriors, and thus obtain bonuses in diamonds also complete a row that will give you many points, but you must organize them as more consecutively as possible or if you cannot be blocked, these actions range from increasing your attack, increasing your movements through the castle towers, mushrooms to control luck, placing books on the towers and incredible powers among others.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At any time you can exchange diamonds with the ghost merchant for useful objects, if it is in solo mode the player must beat a certain score to win, or if there are several players, the player with the most points wins the game by: putting books together, delivering potions to those in charge, for towers that are not destroyed, but there must be a minimum of 2 fog figures, for completed rows among other scores.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
